{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1677-11_111", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Lettre Galante à Madame de F.]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Le Nouveau Mercure Galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", novembre 1677 (tome IX), p. 111-116"}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/note[1]", "tag": "note", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/note[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Il existe une autre édition parisienne, réalisée \"Suivant la Copie imprimée\" par Theodore Girard, dont la pagination diffère."}], "attributes": {"resp": "editor"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[2]", "text": "."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Je pars pour Marseille, & je vous jure, Madame, que j’y vais malgré moy. Vous me fistes hier un portrait que j’emporte dans le cœur, & j’ay peur que ce soit un trait empoisonné que j’emporte."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " Mais dites-moy, ce beau Portrait,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": " L’avez-vous fait d’apres nature ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": " N’avez-vous point feint quelque trait,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": " Pour embellir vostre peinture ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": " Ce teint blanc, & ces blonds cheveux,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": " Cette main, ce bras, cette taille,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": " Cet Esprit tel que je le veux,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": " Qui surprend, qui brille, qui raille,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": " Enfin cet amas sans égal"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": "De belles qualitez, dont mon ame est ravie,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": " Seroit-il dans l’Original,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[12]/text()[1]", "text": " Tel qu’il est dans vostre Copie ?"}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Si cela est, Madame, pour mon repos je ne dois jamais revenir à Aix ; ou plutost j’y dois bientost revenir, car je m’imagine qu’il est doux de perdre son repos pour la Belle dont vous m’avez donné une si riche idée."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " Par tout ce que vous m’avez dit"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": " Vous avez charmé mon Esprit ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": " Vostre Comtesse est adorable :"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais malgré les appas dont vous m’avez charmé,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": " Si bientost je n’en suis aimé,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Je declare d’abord qu’elle n’est point aimable."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Je suis d’un Mestier, où l’on n’aime pas à perdre son temps. Vous sçavez, Madame, que nous autres Gens d’Affaires nous sommes fort interessez, & que jamais nous ne faisons d’avances si nous ne voyons un profit prompt & assuré."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " Jamais à la grosse avanture"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": " Nous ne mettons soins ny soûpirs ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Nous voulons seureté mesme dans nostre usure,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Et pretendons gagner cent pour cent en plaisirs."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": " Sans nul scrupule en Gens fort sages,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Nous nous faisons payer l’interest d’un seul jour,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": " Et comme un Juif nostre amour"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": " Ne preste que sur bons gages."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Il est bon, Madame, de donner cet avis à vostre aimable Comtesse, afin qu’elle examine si mon commerce la peut accommoder. Je reviendray en cette Ville dans quelques jours, & si elle me veut recevoir malgré mes usures amoureuses, j’iray chez elle étaler ma marchandise."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]/text()[1]", "text": "À Aix."}]}]}]}